  "item_count": 13,
  "items": [
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q63",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q63\"\n    title=\"Identificar índice de raíz a partir de exponente fraccionario\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>D</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Considera la siguiente potencia:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <msup>\n          <mn>16</mn>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </msup>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Al escribir esta potencia en forma de raíz, ¿cuál es el índice de la raíz?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>1</mn></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>3</mn></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>4</mn></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 63
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q64",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q64\"\n    title=\"Conversión de exponente fraccionario a raíz enésima en contexto de dinero\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un simulador de inversiones, se analiza un fondo que en un año aumenta su valor en 60 %. Para repartir este aumento en cuatro trimestres iguales, el banco utiliza el siguiente factor de crecimiento trimestral:</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mn>1,6</mn>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n              <mn>4</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa el mismo factor escrito usando una raíz?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <msup>\n                <mn>1,6</mn>\n                <mn>4</mn>\n              </msup>\n              <mn>1</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mn>1,6</mn>\n              <mn>4</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msqrt>\n              <mn>1,6</mn>\n            </msqrt>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <msup>\n                <mn>1,6</mn>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n              </msup>\n              <msup>\n                <mn>1,6</mn>\n                <mn>4</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mfrac>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 64
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q65",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q65\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia de exponente racional a raíz - Slot 65\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un plano, el área de una plaza resulta ser 9 veces el área de otra plaza similar. Para calcular en cuánto se multiplica el largo de cada lado, se usa el factor\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mn>9</mn><mfrac><mn>1</mn><mn>2</mn></mfrac></msup></math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa el mismo factor, escrito usando el símbolo de raíz?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msqrt><mn>9</mn></msqrt></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mroot><msup><mn>9</mn><mn>2</mn></msup><mn>1</mn></mroot></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msqrt><msup><mn>9</mn><mn>2</mn></msup></msqrt></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><msqrt><mn>9</mn></msqrt><mn>2</mn></msup></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 65
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q66",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q66\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia de exponente racional a raíz - Q66\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>Considere la siguiente expresión:\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mrow>\n              <mo>(</mo>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mi>x</mi>\n              <mo>)</mo>\n            </mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>.\n      ¿Cuál de las siguientes opciones corresponde a su forma radical equivalente?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mrow>\n                <mroot>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                </mroot>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msqrt>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                    <mi>x</mi>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n            </msqrt>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 66
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q67",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q67\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia de exponente fraccionario a raíz (tiempo)\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un modelo para describir la posición de un objeto en función del tiempo <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mi>t</mi></mrow></math>, medido en segundos, aparece el factor</p>\n    <p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>5</mn></mfrac></msup></mrow></math>.</p>\n    <p>La estudiante desea escribir este factor usando notación de raíz enésima, sin cambiar su valor. ¿Cuál de las siguientes opciones corresponde a esa conversión?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mroot><mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>5</mn></msup></mrow><mn>2</mn></mroot></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><mroot><mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow><mn>5</mn></mroot></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><msup><mrow><mroot><mrow><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi></mrow><mn>5</mn></mroot></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mrow><msqrt><mrow><msup><mrow><mo>(</mo><mn>3</mn><mi>t</mi><mo>)</mo></mrow><mn>2</mn></msup></mrow></msqrt></mrow></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 67
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q68",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q68\"\n    title=\"Conversión de raíz enésima a exponente racional en contexto científico\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un modelo de física, la magnitud de cierta radiación se expresa como\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mroot>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>E</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>, donde\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>E</mi>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n      representa la energía medida en cierto experimento. Para facilitar los cálculos, se quiere escribir esta expresión usando un exponente racional.</p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones es equivalente a\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mroot>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>E</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>E</mi>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>4</mn>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </mfrac>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>E</mi>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n                <mn>4</mn>\n              </mfrac>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>E</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>E</mi>\n              <mfrac>\n                <mn>1</mn>\n                <mn>4</mn>\n              </mfrac>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 68
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q69",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q69\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia racional a raíz en contexto geométrico\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un taller de geometría, se estudia cómo cambia el volumen de un sólido al escalar una de sus dimensiones. En un modelo, el volumen es proporcional a una medida de longitud \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <msup>\n          <mi>L</mi>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </msup>\n      </math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <msup>\n          <mi>L</mi>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </msup>\n      </math>\n      usando notación de raíz?\n    </p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mroot>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>L</mi>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <msup>\n            <msqrt>\n              <mi>L</mi>\n            </msqrt>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <msqrt>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>L</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </msqrt>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mroot>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>L</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 69
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q70",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q70\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia de exponente racional a raíz\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En una guía de estudio, Gabriela prepara una tabla que compara potencias con exponente fraccionario y sus formas radicales equivalentes. En la primera columna escribe las siguientes potencias:</p>\n    <p>\n      (1)\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mn>64</mn>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n      <br/>\n      (2)\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mn>81</mn>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mn>4</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n      <br/>\n      (3)\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mn>625</mn>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n              <mn>4</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes alternativas podría corresponder correctamente a la segunda columna de la tabla, donde se muestran las formas radicales equivalentes de estas potencias, en el mismo orden?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <p>\n          (1)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <mroot>\n                <msup>\n                  <mn>64</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </mroot>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n          <br/>\n          (2)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <mroot>\n                <msup>\n                  <mn>81</mn>\n                  <mn>3</mn>\n                </msup>\n                <mn>4</mn>\n              </mroot>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n          <br/>\n          (3)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <mroot>\n                <msup>\n                  <mn>625</mn>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                </msup>\n                <mn>4</mn>\n              </mroot>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <p>\n          (1)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <mroot>\n                <msup>\n                  <mn>64</mn>\n                  <mn>3</mn>\n                </msup>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </mroot>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n          <br/>\n          (2)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <mroot>\n                <msup>\n                  <mn>81</mn>\n                  <mn>4</mn>\n                </msup>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </mroot>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n          <br/>\n          (3)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <mroot>\n                <msup>\n                  <mn>625</mn>\n                  <mn>4</mn>\n                </msup>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n              </mroot>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <p>\n          (1)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <msup>\n                <mroot>\n                  <mn>64</mn>\n                  <mn>3</mn>\n                </mroot>\n                <mn>2</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n          <br/>\n          (2)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <msup>\n                <mroot>\n                  <mn>81</mn>\n                  <mn>4</mn>\n                </mroot>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n          <br/>\n          (3)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <msup>\n                <mroot>\n                  <mn>625</mn>\n                  <mn>4</mn>\n                </mroot>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <p>\n          (1)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <msqrt>\n                <msup>\n                  <mn>64</mn>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </msqrt>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n          <br/>\n          (2)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <msqrt>\n                <msup>\n                  <mn>81</mn>\n                  <mn>3</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </msqrt>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n          <br/>\n          (3)\n          <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n            <mrow>\n              <msqrt>\n                <msup>\n                  <mn>625</mn>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </msqrt>\n            </mrow>\n          </math>\n        </p>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 70
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q71",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q71\"\n    title=\"Conversión de exponente racional a raíz enésima en contexto de dinero\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>B</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un informe sobre un fondo de inversión, se indica que el monto final se obtiene multiplicando el capital inicial por el factor \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mfenced open=\"(\" close=\")\">\n              <mn>1,25</mn>\n            </mfenced>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>Si se quiere escribir este factor usando raíz en lugar de exponente fraccionario, ¿cuál debe ser el índice de la raíz?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\"\n        response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>8</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>1</mn>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 71
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q72",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q72\"\n    title=\"Conversión de raíz a potencia con exponente racional en contexto científico\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un informe de física de materiales, una investigadora describe cómo cierta magnitud depende de la longitud característica <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>L</mi></math> de una muestra. En su modelo aparece la expresión</p>\n    <p>\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mroot>\n          <msup>\n            <mi>L</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n          <mn>3</mn>\n        </mroot>\n      </math>\n    </p>\n    <p>Ella quiere escribir esta expresión usando un exponente racional en vez de una raíz. ¿Cuál de las siguientes potencias es equivalente a la expresión anterior?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <msup>\n            <mi>L</mi>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n              <mo>/</mo>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </msup>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>L</mi>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>3</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <msup>\n            <mi>L</mi>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n              <mo>/</mo>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </mrow>\n          </msup>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <msup>\n            <mi>L</mi>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n          </msup>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 72
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q73",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q73\"\n    title=\"Conversión de exponente racional a raíz enésima\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>C</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\" cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un estudio estadístico, la probabilidad de que una persona elija cierta opción se representa por <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>p</mi></math>. En un informe se usa la expresión con exponente fraccionario <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>p</mi><mfrac><mn>3</mn><mn>4</mn></mfrac></msup></math>.</p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones la representa de manera equivalente usando radicales?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mroot><msup><mi>p</mi><mn>4</mn></msup><mn>3</mn></mroot></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mroot><mi>p</mi><mn>4</mn></mroot><mn>3</mn></msup></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mroot><msup><mi>p</mi><mn>3</mn></msup><mn>4</mn></mroot></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msqrt><msup><mi>p</mi><mn>3</mn></msup></msqrt></math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 73
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q74",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q74\"\n    title=\"Detección de error en conversión de potencia a raíz\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En su cuaderno de Matemática, Martina debe reescribir la expresión \n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mn>4096</mn>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>7</mn>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>\n      usando notación de raíz enésima.\n    </p>\n    <p>Martina escribe:\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <msup>\n            <mn>4096</mn>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>7</mn>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <mroot>\n            <msup>\n              <mn>4096</mn>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </msup>\n            <mn>7</mn>\n          </mroot>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>.\n    </p>\n    <p>El profesor sabe que la igualdad es incorrecta. bfCuál de las siguientes afirmaciones describe mejor el error que cometió Martina al hacer esta conversión?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        Intercambió el numerador y el denominador del exponente fraccionario, usando 7 como índice de la raíz y 5 como exponente del radicando.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        Omitió el índice de la raíz y debió escribir una raíz de quinto orden en lugar de la que mostró.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        Dejó el exponente 7 fuera del radical, en lugar de aplicarlo al número 4096 dentro del símbolo de raíz.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        Interpretó el exponente racional\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>7</mn>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </math>\n        como una división de potencias de 4096, en vez de relacionarlo con una raíz enésima.\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 74
    },
    {
      "item_id": "A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q75",
      "qti_xml": "<qti-assessment-item\n    xmlns=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\"\n    xmlns:xsi=\"http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance\"\n    xsi:schemaLocation=\"http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0\n      https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd\"\n    identifier=\"A-M1-NUM-03-08_Q75\"\n    title=\"Conversión de potencia con exponente racional a raíz enésima (tiempo)\"\n    adaptive=\"false\"\n    time-dependent=\"false\">\n  <qti-response-declaration identifier=\"RESPONSE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"identifier\">\n    <qti-correct-response>\n      <qti-value>A</qti-value>\n    </qti-correct-response>\n  </qti-response-declaration>\n  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier=\"SCORE\"\n      cardinality=\"single\" base-type=\"float\">\n    <qti-default-value>\n      <qti-value>0</qti-value>\n    </qti-default-value>\n  </qti-outcome-declaration>\n  <qti-item-body>\n    <p>En un modelo físico, el tiempo de enfriamiento de una pieza metálica se aproxima mediante la expresión\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <mrow>\n          <mi>t</mi>\n          <mo>=</mo>\n          <msup>\n            <mrow>\n              <mn>2</mn>\n              <msup>\n                <mi>h</mi>\n                <mn>3</mn>\n              </msup>\n            </mrow>\n            <mfrac>\n              <mn>4</mn>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mfrac>\n          </msup>\n        </mrow>\n      </math>, donde <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>h</mi></math> es la altura de la pieza en metros.</p>\n    <p>Para explicarlo a estudiantes que solo trabajan con raíces, la profesora decide reescribir\n      <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n        <msup>\n          <mrow>\n            <mn>2</mn>\n            <msup>\n              <mi>h</mi>\n              <mn>3</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n          <mfrac>\n            <mn>4</mn>\n            <mn>5</mn>\n          </mfrac>\n        </msup>\n      </math>\n      usando notación con radical.</p>\n    <p>¿Cuál de las siguientes expresiones representa la misma cantidad de tiempo?</p>\n    <qti-choice-interaction max-choices=\"1\" response-identifier=\"RESPONSE\">\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"A\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                    <msup>\n                      <mi>h</mi>\n                      <mn>3</mn>\n                    </msup>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>4</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>5</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"B\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msup>\n              <mroot>\n                <mrow>\n                  <mn>2</mn>\n                  <msup>\n                    <mi>h</mi>\n                    <mn>3</mn>\n                  </msup>\n                </mrow>\n                <mn>5</mn>\n              </mroot>\n              <mn>4</mn>\n            </msup>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"C\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <mroot>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                    <msup>\n                      <mi>h</mi>\n                      <mn>3</mn>\n                    </msup>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>5</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n              <mn>4</mn>\n            </mroot>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n      <qti-simple-choice identifier=\"D\">\n        <math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\">\n          <mrow>\n            <msqrt>\n              <mrow>\n                <msup>\n                  <mrow>\n                    <mn>2</mn>\n                    <msup>\n                      <mi>h</mi>\n                      <mn>3</mn>\n                    </msup>\n                  </mrow>\n                  <mn>4</mn>\n                </msup>\n              </mrow>\n            </msqrt>\n          </mrow>\n        </math>\n      </qti-simple-choice>\n    </qti-choice-interaction>\n  </qti-item-body>\n  <qti-response-processing\n    template=\"https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/rptemplates/match_correct.xml\"/>\n</qti-assessment-item>",
      "slot_index": 75
    }
  ]
}